OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfcom to investigate David 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FLammy's LBC show           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofcom has announced it has launched an 
OL,6, investigation into a programme hosted  
OL,7, by David Lammy on radio station LBC.   
OL,9,FThe broadcast regulator said it would  
OL,10,Fexamine whether the 29 March (Good     
OL,11,FFriday) episode broke rules on         
OL,12,Fpoliticians acting as news presenters. 
OL,14,FThe shadow foreign secretary has hosted
OL,15,Fa Sunday morning show on the station   
OL,16,Fsince 2022 and also covers for other   
OL,17,Fpresenters on bank holidays.           
OL,19,FBBC News has asked Lammy and Global,   
OL,20,Fwhich owns LBC, for comment.           
